item.description:
@The_Rs_Monkey wrote:

as much sites as u want. srry 

program IEFunScript;
var
 Sites : Array Of String;
 NumOfSitesBelow : Integer;
 I : Integer;

procedure Setup;
begin
NumOfSitesBelow := 2;
setarraylength(Sites,NumOfSitesBelow + 1) //dont change

Sites[1] := 'http://google.com'
Sites[2] := 'http://cruels.net'
end; //You Can Add more

begin
Setup;
repeat
for i := 1 to getarraylength(sites) - 1 do
begin
    movemousesmooth(95, 100);
    wait(500);
    clickmouse(95, 100, true);
    wait(500)
    sendkeys(Sites[i]);
    wait(1000);
    movemousesmooth(901, 100);
    wait(500);
    clickmouse(901, 100, true);
    wait(5000);
end;
until(false)
end.
